text: Jake Kaminski (born August 11, 1988) is an American archer.Jake Kaminski at NBCOlympics.com ; retrieved 2012-8-13. He is best known for competing in the Summer Olympic Games.SportsReference.com (SR/Olympics), "Jake Kaminski" ; retrieved 2012-8-13. ==Career== At the 2012 Summer Olympics, he was part of the men's archery team that won a silver medal. ==Related pages== * United States at the Olympics * Brady Ellison * Jacob Wukie ==References== ==Other websites== * Jake Kaminski at London2012.com Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:American archers Category:Olympic silver medalists for the United States
